  "pageTitle": "面向再生骨料回收的破碎与筛分设备",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-industrial\"> <section class=\"section split-section\"> <div> <p class=\"eyebrow\">C&D 废弃物回收</p> <h1>面向再生骨料回收的破碎与筛分设备</h1> <p class=\"hero-copy\">该蔚澜 Lion One 系统结合了破碎、滚筒骨料筛分、振动骨料筛分、磁性分离、气流分离、打包、称重以及数字控制，适用于 C&D 废弃物、装饰废料、拆除废料和大件废弃物项目。</p> <div class=\"hero-actions\"> <a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/contact\">请求提案</a></div></div> <figure class=\"split-section-media\" aria-label=\"综合建筑废弃物破碎与骨料筛分站视频\"> <video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload=\"metadata\" poster=\"/assets/images/Lion1_boom.png\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/Lion1_boom.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/Lion1_boom.MOV\" type=\"video/quicktime\"> 您的浏览器不支持视频播放。</video></figure></section> <section class=\"section\" id=\"core-parameters\" aria-labelledby=\"core-parameters-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">核心数据</p> <h2 id=\"core-parameters-title\">面向重载破碎、骨料筛分与分离的一体化站</h2> <p>重型移动站面向建筑、装饰、拆除及大件废弃物处理，核心数据按工作范围列出。</p></div> <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"core-parameters-title\"> <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\"> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">综合破碎与骨料筛分站</p></div> <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <div><dt>MFG</dt><dd>蔚澜</dd></div> <div><dt>类型</dt><dd>移动&nbsp;站</dd></div> <div><dt>等级</dt><dd>重型&nbsp;</dd></div></dl></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>处理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-suffix-unit\">t/h</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>进料尺寸</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-suffix-unit\">mm</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>占地面积</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\"><span class=\"spec-suffix-unit\">m<sup>2</sup></span> · 11.7 × 3 × 3.1 m</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>驱动</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">全液压</span></dd></div></dl> <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span> <span>宁波，中国</span> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span> <span>集成移动站</span></footer></article></div></div></section> <section class=\"section\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">工艺模块</p> <h2>回收效果由集成模块、液压驱动与控制系统共同决定</h2> <p>配置支持回收骨料回收、轻质材料分离、金属去除、自动控制和运营报告。</p></div> <ol class=\"industrial-ledger\" role=\"list\"> <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\"> <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-01</span> <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\"> <h3>一体化移动站</h3> <p>集成破碎与骨料筛分站，200 mm进料尺寸，且35 m<sup>2</sup> 车身布局，以及全液压驱动。</p></div> <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\"> <div><dt>稳定给料</dt><dd>200 mm</dd></div> <div><dt>驱动</dt><dd>液压</dd></div></dl></li> <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\"> <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-02</span> <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\"> <h3>产能范围选项</h3> <p>处理能力选项适用于不同规模的市政、工业和 C&D 废弃物资源化项目。</p></div> <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\"> <div><dt>分布范围</dt><dd>20-70 t/h</dd></div> <div><dt>分级</dt><dd>3 等级</dd></div></dl></li> <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\"> <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-03</span> <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\"> <h3>模块化分离工段</h3> <p>覆盖破碎机、C&D 废弃物滚筒筛、用于回收骨料的振动筛、用于 C&D 废料的磁性分离器、用于 C&D 废弃物的正负压气流分离系统以及打包机。</p></div> <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\"> <div><dt>模</dt><dd>6 阶段</dd></div> <div><dt>配置</dt><dd>模块化</dd></div></dl></li> <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\"> <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-04</span> <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\"> <h3>控制系统模式</h3> <p>手动、自动和远程控制模式支持启停控制、警报、称重流量和报告。</p></div> <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\"> <div><dt>模式</dt><dd>手动 · 自动 · 远程</dd></div> <div><dt>控制</dt><dd>PLC + DCS</dd></div></dl></li></ol></section> <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-process-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">工艺流程</p> <h2 id=\"construction-process-title\">建筑废弃物回收处理线宣传视频</h2> <p>观看蔚澜 Lion One 一体化产线以连续系统展示破碎、筛分、输送、分离和资源化回收过程。</p></div> <figure class=\"construction-process-video\" aria-label=\"建筑废弃物回收处理线宣传视频\"> <video playsinline preload=\"metadata\" poster=\"/assets/images/Lion1_boom.png\" controls> <source src=\"/assets/video/Lion1_boom.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/Lion1_boom.MOV\" type=\"video/quicktime\"> 您的浏览器不支持视频播放。</video></figure></section> <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" id=\"comparison\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-compare-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">对比数据</p> <h2 id=\"construction-compare-title\">对比数据覆盖占地、产能、功耗与安装效率</h2> <p>蔚澜集成的C&amp;D废弃物处理线如何与典型的多机场地配置相比，基于驱动总拥有成本的指标。</p></div> <div class=\"product-compare-layout\"> <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"Lion One 爆炸视角\"> <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame is-technical-plate\"><img src=\"/assets/images/Lion1_boom.png\" alt=\"Lion One 爆炸对比视图\"></div> <figcaption> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">集成移动站·重型</span> <dl class=\"product-compare-explode-stats\" aria-label=\"Lion One 摘要\"> <div><dt>占地</dt><dd>35 m²</dd></div> <div><dt>产能</dt><dd>20-70 t/h</dd></div> <div><dt>安装</dt><dd>2-3 天</dd></div></dl></figcaption></figure> <div class=\"product-compare-panel\"> <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>蔚澜 Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-legend\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>GREATWALL HAVEY INDUSTRY MK-F50</span></header> <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\"> <li class=\"product-compare-row\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span> <h3>占地面积</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">集成站的 m²</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:79%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">35 m²</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">44.2 m²</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">集成移动站在单滑架中取代了多机场布局。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span> <h3>处理能力</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">t/h额定范围</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">20-70 t/h</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:88.6%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">40-62 t/h</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">处理能力条按 70 t/h 上限进行归一化展示，标签保留各型号的完整运行范围。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span> <h3>功耗</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">千瓦 / 100 t/h</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:80%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">132 kW</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">165 kW</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">按额定吞吐量计算，每吨分拣功率约降低25%。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span> <h3>运输与组装</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">现场安装天数</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:12%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">2–3 天</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:95%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">18 – 25 天</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">移动站使用标准拖车运输；现场工作主要为定位和接驳。</p></li></ul></div></div></section> <section class=\"section industrial-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-faq-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">常见问题</p> <h2 id=\"construction-faq-title\">规模判断从组成、进料尺寸、工艺模块与场地布局开始</h2> <p>利用这些答案准备骨料回收应用设备的早期供应商比较、内部可行性记录和 RFQ 信息。</p></div> <div class=\"industrial-faq-panel\"> <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\"> <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-01</span> <div> <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">成本与模块范围</h3> <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">成本取决于产能需求、进料量、所需输出、破碎与骨料筛分范围、磁分离、气流分离、打包、控制系统、场地布局以及调试支持。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span> <span>产能依据</span> <span>场地布局</span></div></div></article> <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\"> <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-02</span> <div> <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">可处理物料范围</h3> <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">该处理线用于 C&D 废弃物、装饰废料、拆除废料、大块废料以及需要破碎、骨料筛分、金属回收和轻重分离的混合轻质材料。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span> <span>废弃物组成</span> <span>物料照片或视频</span></div></div></article> <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\"> <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-03</span> <div> <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">集成模块范围</h3> <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">典型的生产线可能包括送料、破碎、滚筒骨料筛分、振动骨料筛分、C&amp;D废弃物磁性分离器、气流分离系统、打包机、称重、PLC 控制和远程监控。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span> <span>所需输出规范</span> <span>需要回收模块</span></div></div></article> <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\"> <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-04</span> <div> <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">产能选择依据</h3> <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">产能应与每小时来料量、物料密度、预期运行时间、产出数据、本地运输节奏和场地占地面积相匹配。蔚澜可以在推荐20-70 t/h配置前查看项目数据。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span> <span>进料尺寸</span> <span>运营时间与运行时间</span></div></div></article></div></section> <section class=\"section industrial-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-rfq-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ 输入资料</p> <h2 id=\"construction-rfq-title\">配置精度取决于组成、进料尺寸、产能与布局输入</h2> <p>使用此 RFQ 清单准备足够的工程背景，用于处理能力选择、模块配置、运输规划和安装评审。</p></div> <div class=\"industrial-rfq-checklist\"> <article> <span>DATA-01</span> <h3>废弃物组成</h3> <p>估算混凝土、砖块、木材、塑料、金属、土壤、装饰废弃物、大块废弃物和轻质杂质的比例。</p></article> <article> <span>DATA-02</span> <h3>进料尺寸</h3> <p>确认最大进件尺寸、平均块状大小、预选状态，以及是否需要预破碎的超大件物料。</p></article> <article> <span>DATA-03</span> <h3>产能依据</h3> <p>共享小时吞吐量、工作班次、预期运行时间、季节性负载变化及最终汇总产品数据。</p></article> <article> <span>DATA-04</span> <h3>场地布局</h3> <p>提供可用占地面积、卡车动线、电力接入、用水与粉尘控制限制，以及出料储存区。</p></article></div> <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\"> <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求工程评审</a> <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">准备文件包</a></div></section></main>"
}
